answers.questionText: Which AWS AI managed service extracts text, tables, and forms from scanned documents?
answers.actualAnswerText: Amazon Textract extracts text, tables, and forms from scanned documents and PDFs using managed document-understanding models.

answers.questionText: Which AWS AI managed service powers semantic search across S3, SharePoint, and database repositories?
answers.actualAnswerText: Amazon Kendra is the AWS AI managed service used for semantic search across S3, SharePoint, databases, and similar content stores.
